dcterms:creator: A. Saxena
K. Goebel
dcterms:description: The C-MAPSS dataset is a benchmark for turbofan engine degradation simulation, providing time series data from multiple sensors capturing the operational behavior of engines until failure.
dcterms:title: C-MAPSS (Commercial Modular Aero-Propulsion System Simulation)

dcterms:creator: A. Saxena
K. Goebel
dcterms:description: FD001 is a subset of the C-MAPSS dataset, containing time series data from 100 instances of a turbofan engine, capturing sensor readings from the beginning of usage until failure.
dcterms:title: FD001

dcterms:creator: A. Saxena
K. Goebel
dcterms:description: FD004 is another subset of the C-MAPSS dataset, containing time series data from 249 instances of a turbofan engine, capturing sensor readings from the beginning of usage until failure.
dcterms:title: FD004
